      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a fair overview, but can you go more into the specific arguments made by those who believe there is a genetic component? Like, what are the actual theories or researchers usually cited when they claim these gaps aren't just environmental? I want to understand the \"hereditarian\" side of the argument better.",
